overview: Once you become a hotwife, there's no reason to go back! Your gorgeous vixens Gianna Dior, AJ Applegate, Alina Lopez and Luna Star love to keep things fresh, new and always exciting. So they've grabbed their favorite stag on the side for that much needed TLC! Don't miss sexy, all-new tales of hotwifing!
title: Stags & Vixens 2
